IMAPStore posteo-remote
Host posteo.de
Port 993
User maeborow@posteo.net
PassCmd "cat /home/maedayscout/.mail-pass"
SSLType IMAPS

MaildirStore posteo-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/email/posteo/
INBOX ~/.local/share/email/posteo/INBOX
Flatten .

Channel posteo
Far :posteo-remote:
Near :posteo-local:
Patterns INBOX Drafts Sent Trash Archive
SyncState *
Create Both
Expunge Both
MaxMessages 0
